        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Want practice-area content + GBP done for you?</h4>
            <p>theStacc publishes 30 SEO articles a month and runs your Google Business Profile. <strong>$167/mo for the bundle</strong> — built for solo and small firms that want consultations, not dashboards.</p>
