            <a href="/demo/" class="cta-btn-inline">See a live demo <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">No card · 15-min walkthrough</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 id="what-is">Why lawyers need different SEO tools</h2>
        <p>Legal SEO breaks into four jobs that generic suites don't fully cover:</p>

        <ol>
          <li><strong>Google Business Profile + local pack</strong> — the single biggest driver of consultation calls.</li>
          <li><strong>Reviews + reputation</strong> — review count and velocity move map pack rankings, period.</li>
          <li><strong>Citation consistency</strong> — NAP across legal directories (Avvo, Justia, FindLaw, state bar listings).</li>
          <li><strong>Practice-area content</strong> — YMYL-grade articles built around real client questions, not keyword fluff.</li>
        </ol>

